scenes.description: Gawr Gura performs 'Treasure Box' by Houshou Marine on a virtual pirate ship stage.
Gura transitions back to her stream setup, chatting with viewers and preparing to show birthday merchandise.
Gura showcases her birthday merchandise, including a tablet case and cable ties.
